question: Give me all engineer jobs and architect jobs that have a salary of 80000
sql_query1:
SELECT Jobs.title 
FROM Jobs
WHERE (Jobs.technicalProfession = "Engineer" OR Jobs.technicalProfession = "Architect") AND Jobs.salary = 80000
sql_query2:
SELECT Jobs.title 
FROM Jobs
WHERE Jobs.technicalProfession = "Engineer" OR Jobs.technicalProfession = "Architect" AND Jobs.salary = 80000
interpretation1: Show all engineer and architect jobs that have a salary equal to 80000
interpretation2: Show all engineer jobs and also provide all architect jobs that have a salary equal to 80000.
